Sponge Cake  2x 6inch

(1)
30g butter
	=> 35g butter (to compe** sugar)
30g milk
	=> 35g milk (to compensate for lost sugar)
1/4tbsp vanille

(2)
3 eggs, room temperature
70g sugar
	=> 45g
7,5g honey
	=> 10g honey
75g cake flour
	added 1/8 tsp baking powder

Whipped cream + mascarpone : like this guy https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gtijnX8JGBg&t=3s
200g mascarpone
	try pot entier next time
1/2tsp vanille
	adjust this to taste
30g sucre
240g creme fouettée épaisse
	try 160g next time

---
Butter and milk in pyrex:
	melt

eggs + sugar : then monter en neige
add honey ten continue mixing
sift flour and add it, mix with spatula
add milk butter mix mix with saptula

170g each

baking time : 15 minutes at first

160C 25-27minutes
	
